songs.lyrics:
Baavra Baavra[4]
Baavra yeh dil mera karta tujhse pyaar re
Baavra yeh dil mera karta tera intezar re
Baavra yeh dil mera maane na kya karun mere yaar vee
Baavra Baavra[2]
Tu jo dekhti mujhe to aisa lagta mere yaar ve
Paa liya sab kuch maine bacha kuch na yaar ve
Baavra Baavra
Tu jo muskurati to aisa lagta mere yaar ve
Duniya khushiyon se bhari gum jaisa kuch na yaar ve
Baavra Baavra[4]
songs.title: 100% Publishing
